---
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>About</title>
  </head>
  <body class="bg-rose-50 min-h-screen font-serif">

    <nav class="fixed top-0 w-full flex gap-6 justify-center py-4 bg-rose-50/80 backdrop-blur-sm text-rose-400 text-sm tracking-widest uppercase">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-green-800 transition">Home</a>
      <a href="/about" class="hover:text-green-800 transition">About</a>
      <a href="/contact" class="hover:text-green-800 transition">Contact</a>
    </nav>

    <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-32 pb-16">

      <!-- Header -->
      <h1 class="text-6xl text-green-800 mb-2 italic">About Me</h1>
    
      <!-- Summary -->
      <section class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-rose-300 mb-3">My Journey</h2>
        <p class="text-rose-400 leading-relaxed">
          My web development journey started 3 years ago when I enrolled into the University of North Florida, studying a bachelors Information Science. Since then 
          I've started an internship at the TNT Dental, being responsible for dev operations for over 150 sites country wide. Outside of educationa and work I am also a local musician 
          for the band Armadillo Operator. After graduating this May I plan to begin many new projects within TNT Dental and other local entrepeneurs, stayed tuned for more.
        </p>
      </section>

      <hr class="border-rose-200 mb-10" />

      <!-- Experience -->
      <section class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-rose-300 mb-6">Experience</h2>

        <div class="mb-6">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline mb-1">
            <h3 class="text-green-800 text-lg">Job Title</h3>
            <span class="text-rose-300 text-sm">October 2023 – Present</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-rose-400 text-sm mb-2 italic">TNT Dental · Houston, Texas</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-rose-400 space-y-1 text-sm marker:text-rose-300">
            <li>Responsible for performing dev op duties for new and existing websites</li>
            <li>Responsbile for maintaining and pushing live over 150 websites</li>
            <li>Initialized and configured blogs for clients</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-6">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline mb-1">
            <h3 class="text-green-800 text-lg">Previous Job Title</h3>

      <hr class="border-rose-200 mb-10" />

      <!-- Education -->
      <section class="mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-rose-300 mb-6">Education</h2>
        <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline mb-1">
          <h3 class="text-green-800 text-lg">University of North Florida</h3>
          <span class="text-rose-300 text-sm">Expected May 2022</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-rose-300 text-sm italic">Bachelor of Science in Information Science and Associates in Digital Marketing</p>
      </section>

      <hr class="border-rose-200 mb-10" />

      <!-- Skills -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-rose-300 mb-4">Skills</h2>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          {["HTML", "Typescript", "Tailwind", "SQL", "Astro", "Node", "React"].map(skill => (
            <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-rose-100 text-green-900 rounded-full text-sm">{skill}</span>
          ))}
        </div>
      </section>

    </main>
  </body>
</html>